title: Community Members Invited to Conversation Regarding Papal Encyclical on the Environment (Lebanon Valley College)
text: ( Source : Lebanon Valley College ) A community conversation regarding Pope Francis ' encyclical on the environment, formally titled Laudato Si, will be held in Miller Chapel on the Lebanon Valley College campus Thursday, Oct . 22 at 11 a.m.
